---
title: Spicy Beef Meatball Vindaloo with Basmati Pilau and Cucumber Raita
description: This spicy Indian number simmers meatballs in a glorious sauce. An aromatic dal spice delivers a full-bodied flavour to the Vindaloo, which is served over fluffed rice.
